name: Pre-COVID Morning Commute
description:
This is a capture of a pre-COVID commute. Never thought something as mundane as an early subway ride would be something I would miss. I await for those small moments observing what strangers wear, read, drink and look like to return. 

Size: 3360 × 1368px
Duration: 00:20s loop
Frame Rate: 30fps
2020 by Tosik
